{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_05_03",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 3話 サニピを世界一のアイドルに",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……まさか\nアイドル、辞めるつもりなんですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No way.\nAre you planning to quit being an idol…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "――え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "サニピに、遙子さんよりふさわしい人なんていない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no one more suitable than you for Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんがいなかったら、サニピも月ストも\nここまで来ることは出来ませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Without you‚ neither Sunny Peace nor Moon Tempest…\nwould have come this far.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "そう、なのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺、今日言いましたよね。遙子さんはチームを\nまとめるのがうまいって。でも、撤回させて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told you today‚ right? Haruko-san‚ you're good at\nleading the team. So please retract that statement.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "え……どうして……？\n私、うまく出来てなかった……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh… Why…?\nDid I do something wrong…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "アイドル、佐伯遙子の魅力はそれだけじゃないからです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san‚ your charm as an idol goes beyond that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "は……はい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……S-sorry?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんはどんな時でも、自分より他の人を思いやって\n最高の笑顔とエールを贈れる、凄いアイドルです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're an amazing idol who always think of others and\ngive the best smiles and cheers…no matter the circumstances.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それにどれだけ元気をもらえたことか……\n俺だけじゃなく、サニピのみんなもファンもです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've all got so much energy from you…\nnot just me‚ but all of Sunny Peace and the fans too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうかな？　そんなに褒められると\nちょっと照れちゃうけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so? I'm a bit embarrassed\nwhen you praise me like that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あと遙子さんの実力は、デビュー当時から本物でした\nきっかけさえあれば、絶対にブレイクしていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ Haruko-san‚ your talent has been genuine since your debut.\nWith the right opportunity‚ you would have definitely broken through.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "そのきっかけが、サニーピースの結成だったと思うんだ\nだから私、凄く幸運だなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think the turning point was the formation of Sunny Peace.\nSo I feel really fortunate…….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "違う。幸運だったのは遙子さんじゃない\n他のみんなです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. The fortunate ones are not Haruko-san\nbut the others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どういう意味……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "デビュー経験のある遙子さんは\n唯一、プロの厳しさを知っていたアイドルでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Among us‚ only Haruko-san had experience\ndebuting as an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "だから、他のみんなをフォローしたり\n先輩としてアドバイスを与えて、導いてきた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Therefore‚ you've been leading‚covering‚\ngiving advice and guiding others…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう。そんな風に言ってもらえて\n凄く嬉しいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you.\nI'm really happy to hear you say that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルとして最高の武器を持っている\n経験もあるし、まとめ役だってこなせる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have the ultimate strenth as an idol.\nYou are experienced and can be a leader.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんはこんなものじゃない。もっと上を目指せる\nなのに、アイドルを辞めるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san‚ you're more than this. You can aim higher.\nYet‚ you're thinking of quitting being an idol…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "辞めないけど？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not quitting‚ am I?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "えっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "だから、辞めないわよ\nどうして私が辞める前提で話が進んでるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I said‚ I'm not quitting.\nWhy are you assuming I'm quitting?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "でも、「心が揺らいでる」とか\n「もっとふさわしい人がいる」とか言うから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you said things like \"my heart wavers\"\nand \"there might be someone more suitable\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "辞めるとは言ってないでしょ？\nここまで来たのにもったいないじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never said I was quitting‚ did I?\nIt would be a waste after coming this far.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
