      "text": "……私、今日の今日まで、心のどこかで疑ってたの\nいつかみんなに置いて行かれちゃうんじゃないかって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Up until today‚ somewhere deep inside me‚ I had doubts.\nI wondered if someday I'd be left behind by everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
