      "text": "さくらちゃんみたいな天性の輝きがある訳じゃない\n怜ちゃんみたいにダンスがうまい訳でもない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't have the natural talent like Sakura-chan…\nI'm not as skilled in dancing as Rei-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
