      "text": "チケット瞬殺だったんだって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard the tickets sold out in an instant‚ is that true?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh025.m4a",
      "text": "はい。これだけ大きな会場なのに……\n嬉しい悲鳴ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Despite of the large venue…\nit's a happily overwhelming response from the fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 280.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
