      "text": "そっか。そうなんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. I see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 291.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 294.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh027.m4a",
      "text": "……え！？　ど、どうして泣くんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh!? Wh-why are you crying!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 294.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 302.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk030.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんごめん、これは嬉し泣きだから\n――{user}君、私、決めたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ sorry‚ it's tears of joy.\n――{user}‚ I've made up my mind. I'm not going to be in Sunny Peace",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 304.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk031.m4a",
      "text": "少しでも長く、じゃなくて、ずっとサニピを続ける\nそして私がサニピを世界一のアイドルにするの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "for just a little longer‚ I'm going to be in it forever.\nAnd I'm going to make Sunny Peace idol in the world!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 314.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh028.m4a",
      "text": "（世界一か。夢みたいな話だ）\n（でも遙子さんが言うと、出来そうな気になってくる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Best in the world… Sounds like a dream.）\n（But when Haruko-san says it‚ it starts to feel possible.）",
